## Update `ErrorControllerTest`

Use the translation keys returned by the controller.

```java
@Test
void technicalError_shouldReturnTechnicalErrorPage() {
    ModelAndView result = errorController.technicalError();

    assertThat(result.getViewName()).isEqualTo("views/ui-error");

    assertThat(result.getModel())
            .containsEntry("pageTitleKey", "error.technical.pageTitle")
            .containsEntry("iconPath", "/images/icons/tools.svg")
            .containsEntry("titleKey", "error.technical.title")
            .containsEntry("messageKey", "error.technical.message")
            .containsEntry(
                    "strongMessageKey",
                    "error.technical.strongMessage"
            );
}
```

